System Overview

The system is a multi-department attendance platform using AI face recognition.

Each faculty logs into the system and can mark attendance for the subjects assigned to them.

Each department has an HOD, who is also a faculty member but has additional administrative permissions.

Students are registered with face images and embeddings, and attendance is automatically marked when faces are detected.

